      Core API
    </h1>

    <p>The CORE API includes all the "prime" extensions. These methods are at the heart of
       Facets. Any application or library that makes use of Facets, you can be sure, supports
       these methods. Also include is the Functor class, which is a Higher Order Message class.
       It is used by a number of methods to provide fluid interfaces.</p>

